2054.subject: HPWE
2054.course_title_long: Prin of Mov for Ind/ w Disab
2054.descrlong: Includes programming in physical education for neurologically and physically impaired individuals in the psychomotor, affective, and cognitive domains. Provides a knowledge of disabilities, an understanding of indicators and contra-indicators related to skill development (including academics), and the ability to teach integrated movement activities to preschool to eighth grade children with disabilities. (Offered spring semester.)
